quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e Й—owdiiji e Й“ulli"
  77,42,E Й“esnaaЙ—e koЙ“e tuuyate
  77,43,"[ЖҒe wi'anee] : \"Г‘aamee yarone, ko newi moЙ—du, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  77,44,Ko non woni ko Men warjorta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en
  77,45,"haray nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  77,46,Гұaame ndakmitaЙ—on setta ko on bannddiiji
  77,47,"haray nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  77,48,SiЙ“e wiyaama ndukЖҙe Й“e ndukЖҙatah
  77,49,"haray nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  77,50,Honde yeewtere caggal oon Й“e goonЙ—inta